body: "Context: hook lifecycle docs claim stats/health/gc call-site coverage but gc currently dispatches read/write hooks only. Approach: update docs-first contract language for gc onIndex behavior then implement gc onIndex dispatch with deterministic warning propagation and add unit/integration coverage."
